~~taber, but i can mention that we give training in translation, we offer
~~reference materials, we offer handbooks on the books of the bible
~~written by translation consultants, we have a journal that we publish
~~especially for translators (the bible translator in english, le sycomore
~~in french, there is a spanish version on-line), and we provide
~~consultants to guide the translators and assist them to achieve
